data.description: This gorgeous ranch home in historic Madison, GA is an almost completely renovated 3 bedroom, 2 full bath located in a lovely, quiet neighborhood. It is a perfect starter home or a permanent home for raising a family. It is nestled in the middle of a cul-de-sac with a fenced in backyard, a large kennel for your dog and a storage building. This home also features new flooring and a neutral color of fresh paint done in 2023 and a bonus room that could easily be converted to an office, gaming room, or extra bedroom. All new light fixtures/ceiling fans in every room along with new door hardware. The kitchen boasts all new appliances throughout! The back deck was also recently totally rebuilt to allow for the quiet enjoyment of the peaceful backyard setting. This energy efficient home is also equipped with new solar panels that drastically reduce those monthly electrical bills. This home is accessible to most everything around town including walking distance to schools, recreation department, aquatic center, the local library, and downtown Madison. No need to drive and look for parking when you can walk to festivals, boutiques, restaurants and coffee shops. Current Arrow Exterminator Contract in place.
